{"tid":973350,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【同股不同權】小米半年禁售期明日解禁　大行唱衰目標價劈42%","createTime":"2019-01-08T05:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T08:06:06.000Z","uid":65346,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"aaed42cfe29209de34a999ed18aaa2348dd977ab","tid":973350,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:42:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190108/59117331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190108%2F59117331&d=uxQRW%2F95UKVTFjEM%2Bk3TSW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=28db5701\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190108%2F59117331&h=f4da5d38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190108/59117331</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港首隻同股不同權的股票小米（1810）今日再跌4%，低見14.46元。小米去年7月9月上市，明日是上市半年，亦是部分投資者及員工認購權可沽貨的日子，據了解，員工平均持有1至5萬股，或會對小米股價做成短期影響。<br />\n小米上市招股價為17元，在兩個星期後升至22.2元創上市新高，但其後股價反覆向下，較最高價跌近一半，與招股價比較則跌約三成。<br />\n摩根大通把小米評級由增持下調至中性，目標也由18元大幅下調至10.5元，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">降幅達42%。</span><br />\n雷軍去年中於上市慶功宴上曾揚言，「要讓在上市首日買入小米公司股票的投資人賺一倍」。認為小米股價首日潛水，完全是受港股市況波動影響，並指「過去小米路演的時候火得不得了，（機構投資者）不停找我要額度。他隨後接受央視訪問時不諱言，對股價破底感到壓力，夜裡不能成眠，「投資者真金白銀投資55億美金（全球公開發售總額），萬一跌得很難看，怎麼出去見人呢？」"},{"pid":"f9d26aa21f386bbfc5f18537675bc124b357efa1","tid":973350,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:51:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd695cc4a9482d15d7f90fe330008447451e5d0e","tid":973350,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:53:37.000Z","msg":"恆指成份股<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4efa006e2ce9049d82639102c05e66d5350665a0","tid":973350,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:56:08.000Z","msg":"小米個估值過高"},{"pid":"3dd36fe1459afae666a77b66d4795d873ab6adbb","tid":973350,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:57:31.000Z","msg":"有冇人諗住低撈？"},{"pid":"fc0a97568520861f918c3bb5edbd4377a5b77bbc","tid":973350,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T08:10:09.000Z","msg":"人人都用小米手機!<br />\n已經入左博反彈!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afaa0f9ad5c102b15603113c1edd5d303ab59ee5","tid":973350,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T08:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係上市cap完水就走佬"},{"pid":"a95fa20bb85c02ba0284356bf9e38447dca00c35","tid":973350,"uid":73048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaed42cfe29209de34a999ed18aaa2348dd977ab","tid":973350,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:42:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190108/59117331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190108%2F59117331&d=uxQRW%2F95UKVTFjEM%2Bk3TSW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=28db5701\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fr